{"tid":1583260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［老老實實］［投票］其實有幾多人預計場運動會持續5-10年","createTime":"2019-09-20T13:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T13:51:45.000Z","uid":263913,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e009b96b8cbfc8cdb86cb45d6b3f2785a242eeef","tid":1583260,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n即使過咗民主法案，但係面對成個香港已經扭曲曬嘅制度，其實一日中共同港共政府未倒台，一日都唔會有真正嘅民主自由<br />\n<br />\n心up啲講句，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港自從6月9號開始已經翻唔倒轉頭，香港正式踏入咗抗爭嘅新時代，唔會再有粉飾太平嘅日子</span><br />\n<br />\n好想知到底有幾多人有呢個覺悟，知道呢一場係真係以年計嘅戰役<br />\n<br />\n意識倒呢一點之後，大家要慢慢開始調整策略<br />\n保持民意、保持對政權嘅怒火，唔可以單單靠黑警濫暴俾彈藥我地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有呢個心理準備，中共必須滅亡，香港定必重光<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無諗過要抗爭咁多年，香港快啲翻翻半年前就好<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n寧鳴而死，不默而生<br />\n<br />\n天佑吾港"},{"pid":"a3b92a709db515d4b762d9639e65e8b9caa91048","tid":1583260,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺"},{"pid":"60a5a8a0b3ac28e200bdbdbb5bd0ae5678f1c5a3","tid":1583260,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG14VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=79d34330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"da209da08f91abd80ee4ca1d21f6116213d6bba7","tid":1583260,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"bc80f9bd743de93da00a567653f79ba65e449ca6","tid":1583260,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"3dd2c770f5a7c2d13174e798e883036539f7e9ed","tid":1583260,"uid":11031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家幫推行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【921】【聽日有兩項重要活動】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1582866</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[和我推1.0] 聽日921行動post專區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583213</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"48a69a0a5a924714d93711f81f86805c62158d93","tid":1583260,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"政府借減碳排放為名，要向中國買電<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"997a89000cf560e10c173380fa0ddee7495955f7","tid":1583260,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T13:45:54.000Z","msg":"自推1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ad24aac078b6300c49ab6989bf31caf1f64a2a","tid":1583260,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-